=== 前使用國 ===
* {{flag|People's Republic of China}}－在當地生產''DShKM''衍生型，命名為「[[54式重機槍|54式重機槍]]」，目前已被[[85式重機槍|85式重機槍]]、[[W-85式重機槍|W-85式重機槍]]和[[89式重機槍|89式重機槍]]所取代。<ref name="miller2001"/>
* {{flag|Czechoslovakia}}－在當地生產''DShKM''衍生型。<ref name="miller2001">{{cite book |first=David |last=Miller |year=2001 |title=The Illustrated Directory of 20th Century Guns |publisher=Salamander Books Ltd. |location=London |isbn=9781840652451}}</ref>
* {{flag|Czech Republic}}：已被[[白朗寧M2重機槍|白朗寧M2重機槍]]所取代。<ref name="jones2009"/>
* {{flag|Finland}}：已被[[NSV重機槍|NSV重機槍]]所取代。<ref name="jones2009"/>
* {{flag|Nazi Germany}}－二戰期間繳獲使用。
* {{flag|DDR}}
* {{flag|Russian Federation}}：已被[[NSV重機槍|NSV重機槍]]和[[Kord重機槍|Kord重機槍]]所取代。<ref name="jones2009"/>
* {{flag|Serbia}}：已被[[NSV重機槍|NSV重機槍]]所取代。<ref name="jones2009"/>
* {{flag|Soviet Union}}<ref name="miller2001"/>
* {{flag|Yugoslavia}}－在當地生產''DShKM''衍生型。<ref name="g3defencemag"/>

===非國家團体===
DShK也是一種廣被[[準軍事組織|準軍事組織]]和[[叛軍|叛軍]]使用的重機槍之一。
* [[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[聖戰者|聖戰者]]
* [[車臣|車臣]]武裝份子
* [[伊拉克|伊拉克]]叛軍<ref name="elite snajper">{{cite book |title=Sniper One |last=Mills |first=Dan|year=2007|chapter=16|publisher=[[Penguin_Group|Penguin Group]]|isbn=978-0-718-14994-9|quote= They were Dshkes, a Russian-made beast of a thing that fires half-inch calibre rounds and was designed to bring down helicopters.| page =192}}</ref>
* [[臨時愛爾蘭共和軍|臨時愛爾蘭共和軍]]<ref>[http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/ira/inside/weapons.html uncovering the irish republican army] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/ira/inside/weapons.html |date=20161212114312 }} pbs.org</ref>
* [[越南南方民族解放陣線|越南南方民族解放陣線]]－[[越戰|越戰]]時廣泛使用。<ref name="miller2001"/>
* [[反卡扎菲勢力|反卡扎菲勢力]]－在[[2011年利比亞內戰|2011年利比亞內戰]]中使用，大部份裝在[[武裝改裝車|武裝改裝車]]上。<ref>[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jr1tm9uMFq4&feature=related Al-Jazeera coverage of Libyan uprising] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jr1tm9uMFq4&feature=related |date=20120318104604 }} Youtube.com</ref>
* [[敘利亞自由軍|敘利亞自由軍]]
